There seems to be 2 channels missing from the FV<br>
universe.<br>
<br>
/join ae<br>
<br>
could be the AE channel to get wizards/enchanters/clerics<br>
and others together to AE FG,Deep,Ssra, Sebilis, Nurga<br>
now that the group xp rules have changed, AEing<br>
isn't such a bad option. Could be fun.<br>
<br>
<br>
/join trials<br>
<br>
The other is a channel to perhaps gather people to make<br>
groups for PoJ trials and Hedge maze runs.<br>
<br>
PoJ trials is easy:<br>
Get a lvl 65ish tank, get a lvl 52+ cleric,<br>
get a 60ish enc or shaman or bard for slow, <br>
then get 3 fast damage dealers (wizards/mages/rogues)<br>
and you can win the execution trial in PoJ.<br>
<br>
<br>
Hedge Maze in PoN?<br>
Get 18 people,<br>
3 groups of 6, each group with a cleric, a tank and a 61+ enchanter(apathy mez), <br>
bards/shammies for AE slow are nice too.<br>
Then the rest are damage dealers. Run the maze easily.<br>
<br>
Thoughts?<br>
