<br>
You could alternate pulls with the cleric using Harmshield and DA respectively and the pet is great for finishing off almost dead mobs at the end of fights to save your AoE nukers some mana.<br>
<br>
Group taps and feeds, etc. Wouldn't hurt to throw in your AoE nukes too I guess but they're very underpowered compared to true AoE nuking classes.<br>
<br>
&quot;optimal&quot; means different things to different people but two common configurations (assuming you can get all these people in one place) are:<br>
<br>
cleric, enchanter, wizard, wizard, wizard<br>
cleric, enchanter, enchanter, wizard, wizard<br>
<br>
usually with one of the wizards being epic-equipped and pulling.<br>
